data.description: This 1 bedroom/1 bath features exposed brick, hardwood floors, and updated appliances. Within walking distance Stevens Square Park and within a 5-minute drive to the city this offers great location and an affordable price. It is a secured building with free laundry, bike racks and storage locker on site in lower level! Walking distance to Eat Street, Minneapolis Institute of Art and Minneapolis College of Art and Design. It's convenient location is ready for you to make it your own OR a rental investment opportunity! Lots of street parking.
